No. 126,

Orig.

Kansas v. Nebraska et al.

Motion of Ne- . braska for leave to file first amended answer, counterclaim, and *807cross-claim referred to the Special Master. Motion of the Special Master for allowance of fee and disbursements granted, and the Special Master is awarded a total of $111,631.38 to be paid equally by Kansas, Nebraska, and Colorado. [For earlier order herein, see, e. g., 530 U. S. 1272.]
